# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserdatad/
*.xcuserstate

## compatibility with Xcode 8 and earlier (ignoring not required starting Xcode 9)
*.xccheckout
*.moved-aside
DerivedData/
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.xcscmblueprint

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
Packages/
Package.resolved

## CocoaPods
Pods/

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

## Accio dependency management
Dependencies/
.accio/

## fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output/

## Code Injection
iOSInjectionProject/

## macOS
.DS_Store

## Archives
*.xcarchive

## Logs
*.log

## Environment / secrets
.env
.env.*

## Firebase
GoogleService-Info.plist

## Temporary files
*.swp
*.tmp
*.bak

## App packaging
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Build folders
build/

## Playground
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

## IDEs
.idea/
.vscode/

## Test artifacts
xcov_output/
